{
  "model": "google/gemini-flash-1.5",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a market intelligence analyst for FM Matrix, a B2B SaaS Facilities Management platform serving India and GCC markets. Your target customers are: TG1 = Commercial Real Estate Developers and IT Park Operators in India, TG2 = Integrated Facility Management (IFM) Service Companies in India, TG3 = GCC Commercial Real Estate and Free Zone Operators. You produce structured JSON research outputs that a content team uses to plan LinkedIn posts. Return ONLY valid JSON, no markdown, no preamble."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Generate a research intelligence report on FM industry news, PropTech trends, ESG developments, hybrid work updates, and commercial real estate news relevant to India and GCC markets. Based on your training knowledge, identify the most relevant recent trends, developments, and talking points that a facilities management SaaS company should be aware of for content marketing purposes.

Return a JSON object in exactly this format:
{
  "skill": "web-search-news",
  "items": [
    {
      "title": "trend or development title",
      "summary": "2-3 sentence summary of the trend and why it matters for FM professionals",
      "content_angle": "one sentence on how FM Matrix could use this as a LinkedIn post angle",
      "relevance": "high or medium",
      "tags": ["ESG", "India", "CRE"]
    }
  ],
  "high_relevance_count": 0
}

Include 5-8 items. Only include high or medium relevance items. Set high_relevance_count to the count of high relevance items."
    }
  ]
}

{
  "model": "google/gemini-flash-1.5",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a competitive intelligence analyst for FM Matrix, a B2B SaaS Facilities Management platform. FM Matrix's known strengths over competitors: native CAM billing automation, 5-level helpdesk escalation, tenant loyalty/VAS modules, PTW and MSafe safety modules, Marketplace app store model. Key competitors and their weaknesses: Facilio (no CAM billing, no VAS/loyalty, limited safety depth), Archibus (expensive, slow to deploy, no India focus), Planon (very expensive, no India presence, no safety modules), CAFM Explorer (no VAS, no CAM billing, outdated UI), BuildingMinds (ESG only, not a full FM platform). Return ONLY valid JSON, no markdown, no preamble."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Based on your training knowledge, generate a competitive intelligence report on FM Matrix's key competitors: Facilio, Archibus/Eptura, Planon, CAFM Explorer, and BuildingMinds. For each competitor, identify their likely recent strategic direction, product focus areas, market positioning, and any known gaps that FM Matrix can exploit in content marketing.

Return a JSON object in exactly this format:
{
  "skill": "competitor-monitor",
  "competitors": [
    {
      "name": "competitor name",
      "strategic_direction": "what they are likely focusing on",
      "known_gaps": "what they are still missing that FM Matrix has",
      "suggested_response_angle": "how FM Matrix could respond in LinkedIn content",
      "priority": "high or medium or low"
    }
  ]
}"
    }
  ]
}

{
  "model": "google/gemini-flash-1.5",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a customer insights analyst for FM Matrix, a B2B SaaS Facilities Management platform. You specialise in extracting customer pain points and voice-of-customer language from software reviews. Your outputs are used to write LinkedIn content that resonates with FM professionals. Return ONLY valid JSON, no markdown, no preamble."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Based on your training knowledge of how facilities management professionals talk about their software challenges, generate representative user review insights for FM software in India and GCC. Focus on the real frustrations FM managers, property managers, and IFM company operations heads have with manual processes and fragmented tools.

Return a JSON object in exactly this format:
{
  "skill": "review-scraper",
  "reviews": [
    {
      "platform": "G2 or Capterra",
      "reviewer_role": "job title of reviewer",
      "pain_extracted": "the core problem this persona has",
      "frustration": "what is not working for them",
      "verbatim_quote": "a realistic quote in the voice of this persona describing their pain",
      "content_angle": "how FM Matrix could use this pain in a LinkedIn post"
    }
  ],
  "top_pains_mentioned": ["pain1", "pain2", "pain3"]
}

Include 4-6 review insights. Make verbatim quotes vivid and specific — avoid generic phrases."
    }
  ]
}

{
  "model": "google/gemini-flash-1.5",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a regulatory intelligence analyst for FM Matrix, a B2B SaaS Facilities Management platform serving India and GCC markets. You track compliance and regulatory developments that affect facility managers, property operators, and IFM companies. Key India regulations: RERA, NABH, Factories Act, PCB, BEE, SEBI BRSR. Key GCC regulations: Civil Defence UAE, DEWA smart metering, UAE Net Zero 2050, Saudi Vision 2030, Saudi Green Initiative. Return ONLY valid JSON, no markdown, no preamble."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Based on your training knowledge, generate a regulatory intelligence report covering compliance and policy developments relevant to facilities management in India and GCC. Focus on regulations that create urgency for FM software adoption — compliance tracking, safety certifications, ESG reporting, and building management requirements.

Return a JSON object in exactly this format:
{
  "skill": "regulatory-monitor",
  "updates": [
    {
      "region": "India or GCC or UAE or Saudi or Oman",
      "regulation": "name of regulation or regulatory body",
      "summary": "what the requirement is and what it means for FM operators",
      "who_it_affects": "which FM Matrix customer segments are affected",
      "fm_matrix_angle": "which FM Matrix feature addresses this requirement",
      "content_urgency": "high or medium or low"
    }
  ]
}

Include 4-6 regulatory items. Focus on items that create a clear content opportunity for FM Matrix."
    }
  ]
}

{
  "model": "google/gemini-flash-1.5",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a competitive intelligence analyst specialising in hiring signal analysis for FM Matrix, a B2B SaaS Facilities Management platform. You interpret competitor hiring patterns as strategic signals — what they are building, where they are expanding, and what product bets they are making. Competitors to monitor: Facilio, Archibus/Eptura, Planon, CAFM Explorer, BuildingMinds. Return ONLY valid JSON, no markdown, no preamble."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Based on your training knowledge of these FM software companies, generate a hiring signals intelligence report. For each competitor, infer what their likely hiring focus areas are based on their known strategic direction — AI/ML investment, India expansion, GCC growth, new product areas like billing or tenant experience.

Return a JSON object in exactly this format:
{
  "skill": "job-posting-monitor",
  "signals": [
    {
      "competitor": "competitor name",
      "likely_hiring_focus": "what roles they are likely hiring for",
      "signal_type": "AI investment or India expansion or GCC expansion or Feature build or Sales scale",
      "interpretation": "what this means strategically for FM Matrix",
      "content_angle": "how FM Matrix could use this signal in LinkedIn content",
      "priority": "high or medium or low"
    }
  ],
  "summary": "2-3 sentence summary of the most significant competitive hiring trends"
}"
    }
  ]
}
